    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you use the contact form or newsletter signup on this website, we collect the information you provide — such as your name, email address, company name, and message content. This data is used solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>
    <p>We do not collect browsing data, cookies, or any tracking information. This website does not use analytics, tracking scripts, or third-party cookies.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <p>Your information is used only for the purpose you provided it:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to your contact or project inquiry</li>
      <li>To send you information you explicitly requested</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We will never sell, share, or rent your personal data to third parties.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your inquiry data for as long as necessary to fulfill your request. If you wish to have your data removed, contact us at kritrajnexera@gmail.com and we will delete it promptly.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Request access to your personal data</li>
      <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, email kritrajnexera@gmail.com.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This website is hosted on a static server. No third-party services process your data beyond standard network routing.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The latest version will always be published on this page with the updated date.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
